node.text: "But if we learned anything from sports, is that no matter how far down we may be, we are never too far down to come back."
The Houston-based rapper brings his workwear touch to Nike SB, adding bandana patterns, rope-style fat laces, and more to the fat-tongued gem.

node.text: The raffle for the @eastsidegolf x Air Jordan 4 is now life. The shoes will officially release on August 7th. Tap the link in our bio to enter.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sneaker News on July 23, 2021 tagging @fxxkvlogvi. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: Best look yet at the upcoming Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG "Handcrated" is here. This Archaeo Brown colorway is scheduled to drop on December 19th; hit the link in our bio for a closer look.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on July 22, 2021. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: Another multi-colored mix appears on the Air Max 97, with tan, red, and aqua green stripes accompanying a bright blue mudguard. Can we get these with Air Max 1 soles, though? Tap the link in our bio to see full official images.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on July 22, 2021. May be an image of footwear and text that says '人 JUL 27 $100 AIR JORDAN 1 LOW "DARK POWDER BLUE"'.

node.text: #SNReleaseAlert : The Air Jordan 1 Low "Dark Powder Blue" will officially release on July 27th, 2021 for $100. Adult and GS sizes confirmed! Tap the link in our bio for full details.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on July 22, 2021. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: Themes of unity have appeared on this upcoming Nike Kyrie 7 for kids. It features a 1 World 1 People logo on the heel with other symbols of peace and love throughout. Tap the link in our bio to see a closer look.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on July 22, 2021. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: The women's Nike Air Max 90 undergoes a full hiking-ready transformation, with extended lacing, textured mudguards, and other minute details giving these a full outdoor aesthetic. Tap the link in our bio for a closer look; these are expected to launch in the Fall.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on July 22, 2021. May be an image of footwear and text that says '1 adidas'.

node.text: ESPN has a rather fitting shoe collaboration coming with adidas and the Top Ten silhouette. The shoes and the box itself are designed with the sports media giant's retro graphics to match the late 70s aesthetic of the silhouette. Tap the link in our bio to learn more.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on July 22, 2021. May be an image of one or more people.

node.text: Rick Owens and Converse produce on of 2021's most daring collaborations yet with the Chuck 70 TURBODRK. Two styles are confirmed to release on July 27th; tap the link in our bio to learn more.

node.text: Founded in 2019, @eastsidegolf embarks upon an official collaboration with Jordan Brand for the Air Jordan 4 Golf. Featuring a familiar white/cement upper, East Golf adds their distinct spin on the model, complete with custom logos and a golden yellow outsole that depicts a scene of admiring fans. For details on how to get a pair of this upcoming collaboration, hit the link in our bio.

node.text: An Air Jordan 1 Low "Green Toe" is coming soon with subtle yellow hits on the Jumpman logo on the tongue. Need these to match with your Pine Green Highs! Tap the link in our bio to see a closer look.

node.text: A first look at the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG WMNS "Atmosphere" has surfaced. These are expected to release on December 22nd. Hit the link in our bio for a closer look.

node.text: The "Bred Toe" look makes a comeback on the Air Jordan 1 Low. An instant classic upon its release in 2018, this fan-favorite color-blocking will be coming soon on the Low-top style. Tap the link in our bio to see a closer look.
